A wrapper around [telebit](https://telebit.cloud/) (A ngrok like service).

# Installation & Usage:


# Follow these steps: 
- 1st: ```git clone https://github.com/Xeroxxhah/telebit-python```
- 2nd: ```cd telebit-python```
- 3rd: ```sudo python3 setup.py install```
